OL,6,FBen's camera almost immediately began
OL,7,Fmoving in the wrong direction, taking
OL,8,Fhis autocue with it. And he did
OL,9,Findeed become dependent on his paper
OL,10,Fscript when the autocue moved too far
OL,11,Faway.
OL,13,FBen completed his link for the
OL,14,Fopening story and the accompanying
OL,15,Fvideo package was then played out
OL,16,Fnormally.
